<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <title>Email Publication Live</title>
</head>
<style type="text/css">

  * {
    margin: 0px;
    padding: 0px;

    color: #000;

    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    background: rgba(155, 219, 213, 0.12);
    width:100%;
    heigth: 100%;
  }

  .flex {
    display: flex;
  }

  .w-100 {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;

    max-width: 640px;
    margin: auto;
    margin-top: 124px;
    padding: 72px;
    padding-right: 0px;
    
    background: #FBFBFB;
  }


  .logo {
    width: 240px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .circle {
    justify-content: center;

    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    padding: 8px;

    background:#63BEB6;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .circle.small {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    padding: 6px;
  }
  .circle.small img {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
  }

  .date-header {    
    margin-bottom: 24px;
        
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: normal;
  }

  .date-header span.date {
    color:#63BEB6;
  }

  .date-header .date {
    margin: auto 0px;
  }

  .date-header .circle {
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .title h1 {
    width: 450px;

    font-size: 25px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 35px;
  }

  .message-contain {
    margin-top: 56px;
  }

  .message-contain h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;

    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 24px;
  }

  .message-contain p {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 24px;
  }

  .message-contain p .info {
    color: #767676;
  }

  .event {
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .event-indicator {

    width: 24px;
    margin-right: 24px;
  }

  .event-indicator .indicator {

    width: 1px;
    height: 12px;
    margin: auto;

    background: #63BEB6;
  }

  .event-contain .title .name {
    color: #63BEB6;

    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 24px;
  }

  .event-contain .title .date {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 25px;
  }

  .event-contain .social-media p {
    color: #767676;
    margin-right: 12px;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 24px;
    margin: 0px 16px;

    background: #767676;
  }

  .contain-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    margin: 48px 0px;

    background: #ebebeb;
  }

  .button-link {
    display: block;
    width: max-content;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding: 10px 16px;

    color: #fff;
    background: #222525;
    border-radius: 8px;

    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .marketing-info {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 25px;
  }
  

</style>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <div class="logo-container">
    <img class="logo" src="/assets/campaign-centric-logo.svg" alt="">
  </div>
  <div class="flex">
    <div class="left">
      <div class="flex w-100 date-header">
        <div class="flex circle">
          <img src="{{imagesUrl}}/assets/calendar-today.svg" alt="">
        </div>
        <span class="date">{{publicationDateTime.date}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="title">
        <h1>{{brandName}} - <br> Your publication is live!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="message-contain">
        <h2>Hey there, {{businessOwnerName}}!</h2>
        <p>Your publication scheduled for today has been launched:</p>
        <div class="flex event">
          <div class="event-indicator">
            <div class="flex circle small">
              <img src="{{imagesUrl}}/assets/verified.svg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="indicator"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex w-100 event-contain">
            <div class="flex title">
              <h3 class="name">{{publicationName}}</h3>
              <div class="divider"></div>
              <h3 class="date">{{publicationDateTime.hour}}</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>If you’ve set up auto-publish, campaign-centric pushed these publications to the social media accounts you chose.
          <br><br>
          If you selected a print format, it’s time to publish it.
          <br><br>
          For more info about your publication, go to campaign details.
          <br><br>
          <span class="info">You can also download your publications, and post them manually. <br>Print publications must be handled manually in your campaign.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
      <img src="{{imagesUrl}}/assets/shape.svg" alt="" class="shape">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="contain-divider"></div>
  <a class="button-link" href="{{link}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Go to campaign details</a>
  <h3 class="marketing-info">Marketing campaigns made easy.</h3>
</div>

</body>
</html>